QuizMaster – Science Grade 9
</h1>

<div id="quizBox"></div>

<div class="mt-4 flex justify-between">
<button onclick="prevQuestion()" class="bg-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded">Previous</button>
<button onclick="nextQuestion()" class="bg-maroon-600 bg-[#800000] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">Next</button>
</div>

<div class="mt-4 text-center">
<button onclick="resetAttempts()" class="text-sm text-red-600 underline">Reset Attempts</button>
</div>

